       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ORDERPGM.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT ORDER-FILE ASSIGN TO ORDFILE.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY ORDREC.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARA.
           PERFORM READ-ORDER
           PERFORM CALC-TOTAL
           STOP RUN.
       READ-ORDER.
           READ ORDER-FILE INTO ORDER-RECORD.
       CALC-TOTAL.
           COMPUTE WS-TOTAL = ORD-QTY * ORD-PRICE.
